{"tid":1762841,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[習敗敗]原來無論讓唔讓步，中國人都會學香港抗爭","createTime":"2019-11-30T01:23:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T01:27:36.000Z","uid":132859,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"108875d948cfc4e121545f1b7e7920e24d96dab5","tid":1762841,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T01:23:11.000Z","msg":"本身話對香港讓步就令中國人學香港抗爭<br />\n所以唔可以退讓<br />\n但依家冇退讓，制度缺陷依然令中國人上街抗爭<br />\n而因為香港，世界對中國嘅抗爭更關注<br />\n中共反而更被動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本大家都唔鍾意個制度<br />\n中共制度有問題就只識用暴力解決<br />\n再鳩up話要穩定<br />\n去正當化自己暴力<br />\n唔肯去理性思考讓步可行性<br />\n咪收唔到科囉<br />\n<br />\n根本要維穩<br />\n就要大事化小 息事寧人<br />\n快手啲應承五大訴求咪好囉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#ha、#dog<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5a1efa12123a15aa5db7eb7dd6f757394b0ead3","tid":1762841,"uid":274136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T01:27:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6hE9ADA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6hE9ADA.jpg&h=be8cfb76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>運動未完 仍需努力</strong></span><br />\n12月8 民陣轉咗遊行"}]}